reviewText: The original Harbinger book and DVD are great. This DVD gives you only one part, with the promise of more. This DVD is a little more technical. The author is in a conference setting talking about what is going to happen next and he believes he will have 6 more sessions. This DVD contains the first session and talks a lot about financial ramifications. Maybe I will have a better opinion after I see all 6 sessions. Also, he does not tell you how or when the next sessions will be available. I will probably write to him or his publishers.
